         <div class="second-banner-description">
             <h2>Creating a </br>
             world of good.</h2>
             <p> Nobly is an app for iOS and Android that allows you to create and contribute to a chain-reaction of kindness. Each Deed tells a story, and with Nobly you can share that story with others and allow them to pay it forward with a Deed of their own.
